koohiiStory1: There are two types of birds often compared to husbands. Yes there are a few vultures out there, but most husbands are CHICKENS. 鶏 【にわとり】 (n) (domestic) chicken, (P) 鶏肉 【けいにく】 (n) chicken meat, (P).
koohiiStory2: The vulture´s husband is a chicken...heck...who am I to judge their interspecies love? They´re both birds so its cool.
